data.title: Ship «Mustai Karim» – navigation and prices 2024
data.meta_description: Vodohod: Ship «Mustai Karim» Sea cruises and river cruises in Russia - «Vodohod»
data.text:
The luxurious Mustai Karim is the newest addition to the fleet on Russian River cruise market. The ship is designed as a "floating hotel" and combines advanced cruising technology with 5* hotel luxury to create a river cruising experience like nothing else. With four beautiful decks to explore, you’ll find something to fill every moment on board.

Mustai Karim was designed by the Marine Engineering Bureau and built at the Krasnoye Sormovo shipyard in Nizhny Novgorod. The motor ship was launched in 2020. The launch of this ship into operation was a unique event for the entire shipbuilding and cruise industry of Russia. The ship public areas include an expansive panorama lounge with a bar, conference hall for onboard lectures and entertainment, wine library, spa with massage salon, sauna and hammam, fitness room, hair salon and medical room with onboard doctor. Guests can enjoy a number of bars of diffirent specialities and two main restaurants for fine dining. Two lifts serving all decks provide the additional comfort onboard. Wi-Fi access is available throughout the ship.
